Q. How can I use loop points stored into WAV files by Convert?

A. Convert store loop points into WAV files as CUE points. You can manipulate
loop points from programs let's you work with this CUE points (standard WAV
specification). Some of these programs are Cool Editor (select the "Loop Range" 
CUE point), and GoldWave (select the "Loop Start" and "Loop End" CUE points).

